  "detailed_description": "<h1>EA版本说明</h1><p>游戏中尚有大量未完成内容！当前游玩过程中可能遭遇各种不良体验！包括不限于各类BUG、引导说明不足、战斗数值粗暴、词条效果不正确、性能优化欠缺等！<br>我们对此先表示歉意！正努力开发优化中！若您遇见任何问题，还请加群向我们反馈！万分感谢！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/bcced0c1dd95a1f510e7025c62999b13.avif?t=1717123454\" width=616 height=1150 /></span></p><br><h1>联系我们</h1><p>玩家QQ群1：854816618（已满）<br>玩家QQ群2：780350096<br>玩家QQ群3：732055609<br>玩家QQ群4：465707574<br>加入我们，请发送简历至 <a href=\"mailto:wukangye@dongyou.com\">wukangye@dongyou.com</a></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>我们想要玩一款能战得过瘾、搭BD搭得过瘾的仙侠游戏，可市面上没有……<br>于是尝试着做了这款《道衍诀》<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/0c8c7aa41b8f0a9adddd461b151f4268.avif?t=1717123454\" width=600 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/d21d9e03981cfb29ba11e756a65f2bde.poster.avif?t=1717123454\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/d21d9e03981cfb29ba11e756a65f2bde.webm?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/d21d9e03981cfb29ba11e756a65f2bde.mp4?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>190</strong>种灵法技能、<strong>200 </strong>种神通被动、<strong>300</strong> 种装备词条</li></ul>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>构建属于你的<u><strong>最强流派</strong></u></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/8d90180d3607101b2da84666eee359df.avif?t=1717123454\" width=600 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/36e7f343841663426e18428f5b15bf47.poster.avif?t=1717123454\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/36e7f343841663426e18428f5b15bf47.webm?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/36e7f343841663426e18428f5b15bf47.mp4?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游荡道精、废弃阵法、天外秘境、道则秘境、数十座宗门与城市，等你发现与探索！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/3b03191f4f5ade450345c5453d2805e2.avif?t=1717123454\" width=600 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/986608b1d17b45acae8174dbff9ebb6a.poster.avif?t=1717123454\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/986608b1d17b45acae8174dbff9ebb6a.webm?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/986608b1d17b45acae8174dbff9ebb6a.mp4?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>是<i>探索收集、凝炼灵石</i>以积累财富？还是<i>炼丹炼器、修炼突破</i>以强化自身？亦或是<i>剿灭妖魔</i>以战养战？</li></ul>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在<strong><u>寿命</u></strong>有限的情况下，你需要规划好每一季度的安排。</li></ul>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>寿命不足，未能破境，<u>会挂</u>；成功突破，落下病根，<u>会挂</u>；死战获胜，根基破损，<u>还会挂</u>！仙途残酷，斟酌你的决策！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/dd5f3f051a9c3548badbab3add707f97.avif?t=1717123454\" width=600 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/8fbe3866839793bee8c750351b7b9679.poster.avif?t=1717123454\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/8fbe3866839793bee8c750351b7b9679.webm?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/8fbe3866839793bee8c750351b7b9679.mp4?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/19f37fadcc9510356e8ce885298f46e5.avif?t=1717123454\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>与预设或随机生成的各式NPC进行交互，你可以：</li></ul>        •  <strong><u>舔</u></strong>他们，交友互赠礼物、交流修道心得<br>        •  <strong><u>泡</u></strong>他们，做个海王（小心情敌！）<br>        •  <strong><u>弄</u></strong>他们，偷、抢、杀、下毒后再杀（不怕举世皆敌的话）<br>        •  <i><u><strong>同时，小心那些邪恶的NPC弄你！</strong></u></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/8bf6e9d53e0b98534b9b9565507207a3.avif?t=1717123454\" width=600 height=93 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/dea5e3b1cda1198738c40421efb8098d.poster.avif?t=1717123454\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/dea5e3b1cda1198738c40421efb8098d.webm?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1951220/extras/dea5e3b1cda1198738c40421efb8098d.mp4?t=1717123454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>妖族正在大举入侵！击败他们！反攻妖界，灭其天道，据其位面！</li></ul></li></ul>",
